According to Table 6 and Table 10, it is clear that Tsallis and t-entropy, two famous objective functions for standard color pictures, outperform for every PIOA over characteristics such as fitness function fÂ¯\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym}
				\usepackage{amsfonts}
				\usepackage{amssymb}
				\usepackage{amsbsy}
